    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create a lash of lightning energy that strikes at one creature of your choice that you can see within 15 feet of you. The target must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pulled up to 10 feet in a straight line toward you and then take [[/damage 1d8 type=lightning]] damage if it is within 5 feet of you.</p><p>This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d8]] when you reach 5th level ([[/damage 2d8]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8]]).</p></div>",
